<plot>The film Jetzt und alle Zeit (Now and for all times) is a description of a day in the life of the "Sisters of Bethania". Jetzt und alle Zeit is not a filmic commentary on the topic "cloister", but rather the attempt to draw, in a documentary fashion, a condensed picture in time of a lived and ritualized form. (Astrid Ofner)</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?276327</url></doc>
